### DentFlow Patients API Tests
### Base URL: http://localhost:5199
### All endpoints require Authorization header (JWT Bearer token)

@baseUrl = http://localhost:5199/api/v1
@authToken = Bearer REPLACE_WITH_VALID_JWT

### ✅ Happy path — Create patient (201)
POST {{baseUrl}}/patients
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: {{authToken}}

{
  "firstName": "John",
  "lastName": "Doe",
  "dateOfBirth": "1985-06-15",
  "gender": "Male",
  "phoneMobile": "+1234567890",
  "email": "john.doe@example.com",
  "addressLine1": "123 Main St",
  "city": "Anytown",
  "stateProvince": "CA",
  "postalCode": "90210",
  "countryCode": "US"
}

###

### ✅ Happy path — Get patient by ID (200)
GET {{baseUrl}}/patients/00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000001
Authorization: {{authToken}}

###

### ✅ Happy path — List patients (200)
GET {{baseUrl}}/patients?page=1&pageSize=10
Authorization: {{authToken}}

###

### ✅ Happy path — Update patient (200)
PUT {{baseUrl}}/patients/00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000001
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: {{authToken}}

{
  "firstName": "John",
  "lastName": "Smith",
  "dateOfBirth": "1985-06-15",
  "gender": "Male",
  "phoneMobile": "+1234567890",
  "email": "john.smith@example.com",
  "status": "Active"
}

###

### ✅ Happy path — Delete patient (204)
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/patients/00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000001
Authorization: {{authToken}}

###

### ❌ Validation error — Create patient with missing required fields (400)
POST {{baseUrl}}/patients
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: {{authToken}}

{
  "firstName": "",
  "lastName": ""
}

###

### 🔒 Unauthorized — No token (401)
GET {{baseUrl}}/patients

###

### 🔍 Not found — Get non-existent patient (404)
GET {{baseUrl}}/patients/00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000000
Authorization: {{authToken}}

